Package: notsooriginal
Architecture: any
Depends: libapache2-mod-raii (>= 0.99), libmagick++9-dev, libexiv2-dev, libcurl4-openssl-dev
Description: a wonderful image gallery for libapache2-mod-raii
 * NotSoOriginal is not O.R.I.G.I.N.A.L.
 * NSO is a bunch of C++ code lines to get your photos on the web
 * The aim of NSO is to handle your directories of digital photos
   without extra files for comment and descriptions. Therefor you
   can put photographs in the directory with DAV or directly with
   your digital still camera/scanner.
 * preview and thumbnails are auto generated when you first hit
   a new or updated image.
 * You can create albums and link photo to them. (virtual directory
   and photos)
 * It handles anonymous, granted and privileged users.
 * You can configure your directories as public, private and hidden.
 * view and hires download count
 * Comment and description.
 * Pour les fran√ßais, vous pouvez envoyer les photos qui vous plaisent
   chez PHOTO-SERVICE pour tirage
